# Blog trust & quality (Cursor)

**Hub:** [`docs/BLOG_TRUST_AND_QUALITY_ROADMAP.md`](docs/BLOG_TRUST_AND_QUALITY_ROADMAP.md)

## Roles

- **AG:** KO/EN/JA, fact sheets, tier-1 URL fixes, UNCERTAIN 해소
- **Cursor:** `pnpm validate:post`, trust gates, INDEX validate column, gate code
- **User:** git commit / deploy only when asked

## Priority

1. **P0** before merge: AG 2.5b → Cursor Phase 3 ([`CURSOR_PHASE3_REVERIFY_PROMPT.md`](docs/CURSOR_PHASE3_REVERIFY_PROMPT.md))
2. Do not mass-edit slugs while AG 2.5b is in progress on the same slug
3. **UNCERTAIN = hard block** — no warning-only bypass

## Validate

```bash
pnpm validate:post <slug>              # includes trust (T1–T3)
SKIP_TRUST_VERIFY=1 pnpm validate:post <slug>   # format gates only
pnpm trust:verify-sources <slug>       # T3 only
pnpm validate:batch                    # 35, skips build + trust
```

## Fact sheet

- `docs/fact-audit/<slug>.md` required when KO has numerics
- No generic `.go.jp/` homepage as sole source with ✓
- Regenerate INDEX: `pnpm trust:update-index`

## Commits

Do not commit unless the user explicitly requests.
